#: ../../simulator/build.md:89 23747414d77f4195ab0fa91593a7d6cc
msgid "The following CMAKE options can be set for the executable configuration:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../simulator/build.md:90 bfea17f6dd1d440985a45af46c4b7b0b
msgid ""
"`USE_SIRIUS_SHARED` (default = OFF): If active, the project will link "
